<p dir="auto"><a href="https://github.com/csstools/postcss-plugins/tree/main/plugins/postcss-focus-within">PostCSS Focus Within</a> duplicates rules using the <code>:focus-within</code> pseudo-class
with a <code>[focus-within]</code> attribute selector, the same selector used by the
focus-within polyfill. This replacement selector can be changed using the
<code>replaceWith</code> option. Also, the preservation of the original <code>:focus-within</code>
rule can be disabled using the <code>preserve</code> option.</p>
